dict.string: Welcome to the Music and Emotion experiment
Please tap twice to continue to the experiment

Make yourself comfortable. While listening to the music please look at the cross at the screen and try not to move or blink your eyes. After you listen to each music excerpt we will ask you to rate on a scale of 1 (very low) to 7 (very strong) the presence of four emotions: happiness, anger, serenity and sadness. The experiment will start with recording your baseline state for 2 minutes. Try not to move while we are recording your baseline
